{"parse":{"title":"On-the-Job Training (OJT)","pageid":2918,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"urn:mrn:iala:dic:0901023e\">urn:mrn:iala:dic:0901023e</a></b>\n</p><p>On-the-job training (<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"9a8153b0eec0bfe3bab70c139c53b83b\">OJT</span>) is training and familiarization at the <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span> centre at which the person will be employed. It includes training on the purpose of the <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span>, the <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span> procedures, facilities and equipment used as well as the local geography and appropriate regulations and other procedures.\n</p><p>Source: \n<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Guideline G1156 Recruitment, training and assessment of <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span> Personnel\n</p><p><br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/Accident\" title=\"Accident\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"9a8153b0eec0bfe3bab70c139c53b83b\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>On-the-Job Training\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Vessel Traffic Services\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615101418\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.031 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.037 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 58/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 623/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 112/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    9.601      1 Template:Languages\n100.00%    9.601      1 -total\n 64.66%    6.208      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:2918-0!canonical and timestamp 20260615101418 and revision id 8651. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"9.1_VTS_terms"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Alphabetical_Index"},{"sortkey":"","*":"IALA_Dictionary_2023_Revision"}]}}